title: "O"RIGINAL SURF HAT- Black
body_html:
Surf Hat 

Made for the water.  Unstructured hat made from UV resistant quick dry nylon.   Proprietary polywrap elastic and turnbuckle back closure.  The back closure on each hat we make is done by hand in our studio.  

Product Details

  • Color: Black
  • Unstructured Cap
  • 100% Nylon 
  • Quick Dry
  • Elastic ploy wrap back band
  • Signature OLA CANVAS closure
 

Hat Sizing

SM: 6 3/4 - 7 1/4

L/XL: 7 1/4 -7 3/4


Designed in California by OLA CANVAS

title: Blackball Boardshort- Black
body_html:
Performance boardshort constructed from a proprietary technical fabric aligned with our guiding principles. Heavier weight(but not heavy) with unparalleled stretch and durability. Made from 80% recycled polyester combined with 20% high grade spandex. Internal waistband is finished with a quick dry fabric with a dobby weave for less cling and more comfort.  Invisible back pocket, finished with a low profile zipper and bungee pull.  The drawcord goes 360 degrees around the waistband and finishes in the front with 4 brass grommets.

Product Details

  • Color: Black
  • 17" out-seam
  • 80% recycled polyester 20% spandex 
  • Back stealth pocket with bungee pull 
  • Internal 360 degree drawcord for full lockdown in water environments. Finishes in front with 4 brass grommets 
  • Easy fly


Designed in California by OLA CANVAS

body_html:
The dockside chino is 100% U.S. made.  Constructed from Mount Vernon Mills 14oz cotton canvas.  This chino has a relaxed fit with a clean taper all the way to the leg opening creating a modern workwear look.  The crop is slightly less than our Utility Pant01 and has more of a taper. It is built using denim machines and construction methods to create a timeless piece that will last for years to come.  Made in Los Angeles, CA

Product Details

  • Color: Desert Tan
  • 14 oz cotton canvas
  • Front slash pockets w/ sewn in gussets for easy clipping of tools
  • Side detail w/ brass O ring for clip on storage 
  • Slightly cropped and tapered leg

title: Dockside Chino - Pre Release
body_html:
The dockside chino is 100% U.S. made.  Constructed from Mount Vernon Mills 14oz cotton canvas.  This chino has a relaxed fit with a clean taper all the way to the leg opening creating a modern workwear look.  The crop is slightly less than our Utility Pant01 and has more of a taper. It is built using denim machines and construction methods to create a timeless piece that will last for years to come.  Made in Los Angeles, CA

Product Details

  • Colors: Birch, Desert Tan, Moss
  • 14 oz cotton canvas
  • Front slash pockets w/ sewn in gussets for easy clipping of tools
  • Side detail w/ brass O ring for clip on storage 
  • Slightly cropped and tapered leg


Designed in California by OLA CANVAS

title: Dockside Chino - Sail
body_html:
The dockside chino is 100% U.S. made.  Constructed from Mount Vernon Mills 14oz cotton canvas.  This chino has a relaxed fit with a clean taper all the way to the leg opening creating a modern workwear look.  The crop is slightly less than our Utility Pant01 and has more of a taper. It is built using denim machines and construction methods to create a timeless piece that will last for years to come.  Made in Los Angeles, CA

Product Details

  • Color: Sail
  • 14 oz cotton canvas
  • Front slash pockets w/ sewn in gussets for easy clipping of tools
  • Side detail w/ brass O ring for clip on storage 
  • Slightly cropped and tapered leg

title: Natural Bonzer Surfboard Bag
body_html:
BONZER

This bag is called the Bonzer as a homage to the classic fuller nose Bonzer style surfboards. The Bonzer bag is specifically designed to work well with full-nose and alternative shapes.  This tough duck canvas bag features a large fin pocket appropriately sized to accommodate up to a 10" fin as well as other items such as wax or sunscreen. 

Product Details

  • Color: Natural (Off White)
  • 15oz cotton duck canvas PFD (prepared for dye) 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Cinch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware: Marine grade brass grommets and snaps

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.  Note: for boards with large single fins we suggest that you size up 4"-6". The extra material will ensure the bag fits over your fin. Bag width ranges from 23" to 25.5".

 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by

title: Natural Full Nose Short Board Bag
body_html:
PFD Natural 

15oz Cotton Duck Canvas 

Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G

Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon Pelican Rope with poly core.

Synch/Toggle: Aluminum Crimp Sleeve 

Hardware: 100% marine grade brass grommets

This bag is specifically design to work well for shortboards with fuller noses. (i.e. hypto crypto, baby buggy, biscuit...) Bags are measured from side seam to side seam for width measurement and the number on the bottom left represents the length of the bag from tip of nose to hem stitch. (not the bottom of the bag) which allow's for two more inches of coverage. Designed and made in Costa Mesa CA by 

OLA Canvas

title: Natural Round Nose Surfboard Bag
body_html:
Round Nose 

The Round Nose bag is specifically designed for -you guessed it- round nose boards. Built to accommodate mid-lengths and longboards, this tough duck canvas bag features a large fin pocket appropriately sized to accommodate up to a 10" fin and other small items such as wax or sunscreen. 

Product Details

  • Color: Natural (Off White)
  • 15oz cotton duck canvas PFD (prepared for dye) 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Cinch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware: Marine grade brass grommets and snaps

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.  Note: for boards with large single fins we suggest that you size up 4"-6." The extra material will ensure the bag fits over your fin. Bag width ranges from 24" to 26".  Starting with 24" for 5'8" bags and ending with 26" for 9'6" bags.

 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by

title: Natural Round Nose Surfboard Bag w/ Fin Slit
body_html:
Round Nose 

The Round Nose bag is specifically designed for -you guessed it- round nose boards. Built to accommodate mid-lengths and longboards, this tough duck canvas bag features a large fin pocket appropriately sized to accommodate up to a 10" fin and other small items such as wax or sunscreen. 

Product Details

  • Color: Natural (Off White)
  • 15oz cotton duck canvas PFD (prepared for dye) 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Cinch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware: Marine grade brass grommets and snaps

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.  Note: for boards with large single fins we suggest that you size up 4"-6." The extra material will ensure the bag fits over your fin. 

 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by 

OLA Canvas

title: Natural Shortboard Bag
body_html:
Shortboard

The go-to bag for your everyday shortboard.  Specifically tailored to fit most modern shortboard designs.  Slightly fuller in the nose and a little wider in width.  This bag also features a fin pocket to hold your board's fins and other small items such as wax or sunscreen.  

Product Details

  • Color: Natural (Off White)
  • 15oz cotton duck canvas PFD (prepared for dye) 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Cinch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware: Marine grade brass grommets and snaps

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.  Bag width ranges from 21" to 23."

 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by

title: Navy Blue Bonzer Surfboard  Bag
body_html:
BONZER

This bag is called the Bonzer as a homage to the classic fuller nose Bonzer style surfboards. The Bonzer bag is specifically designed to work well with full-nose alternative shapes.  This tough duck canvas bag features a large fin pocket appropriately sized to accommodate up to a 10" fin as well as other items such as wax or sunscreen. 

Product Details

  • Color: Navy
  • Water repellent 15oz cotton duck canvas 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Synch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware: 100% marine grade brass grommets and snaps

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.  Note: for boards with large single fins we suggest that you size up 4"-6." The extra material will ensure the bag fits over your fin. 

 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by 

OLA Canvas

title: Navy Blue Full Nose Short Board Bag
body_html:
Navy Blue Water Repellent

15oz Cotton Duck Canvas 

Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G

Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon Pelican Rope with poly core.

Synch/Toggle: Aluminum Crimp Sleeve 

Hardware: 100% marine grade brass grommets

This bag is specifically design to work well for shortboards with fuller noses. (i.e. hypto crypto, baby buggy, biscuit...) Bags are measured from side seam to side seam for width measurement and the number on the bottom left represents the length of the bag from tip of nose to hem stitch. (not the bottom of the bag) which allow's for two more inches of coverage. Designed and made in Costa Mesa CA by 

OLA Canvas

title: Navy Blue Round Nose Surfboard Bag
body_html:
Round Nose 

The Round Nose bag is specifically designed for -you guessed it- round nose boards. Built to accommodate mid-lengths and longboards, this tough duck canvas bag features a large fin pocket appropriately sized to accommodate up to a 10" fin and other small items such as wax or sunscreen. 

Product Details

  • Color: Navy
  • Water repellent 15oz cotton duck canvas 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Synch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware: 100% marine grade brass grommets and snaps

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.  Note: for boards with large single fins we suggest that you size up 4"-6." The extra material will ensure the bag fits over your fin. 

 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by 

OLA Canvas

title: Navy Blue Shortboard Bag
body_html:
Shortboard

The go-to bag for your everyday shortboard.  Specifically tailored to fit most modern shortboard designs.  Slightly fuller in the nose and a little wider in width.  This bag also features a fin pocket to hold your board's fins and other small items such as wax or sunscreen.  

Bags are measured from side seam to side seam for width measurement and the number on the bottom left represents the length of the bag from tip of nose to hem stitch. (not the bottom of the bag) which allow's for two more inches of coverage. 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by 

OLA Canvas

title: OG Boardshort- Black
body_html:
OG BOARDSHORT

Our first boardshort, the OG is made from one of the first tried and true materials for water.  100% Nylon Multi-Ply Taslan. This short has a 16" outseam.  Back patch pocket with button flap closure. Drawstring front closure with button fly. Sizes are hand stamped on interior waistband. Sewn and constructed in Costa Mesa, CA

Product Details

  • Color: Black
  • 100% Nylon taslan weave
  • Outseam 16"
  • Back pocket 
  • Button fly with drawstring closure
  • CA Flag patch on reverse side of left leg 

Designed in California by OLA CANVAS

title: OLA CANVAS x PRETTY BALLADS  BLK/ORG
body_html:
DESCRIPTION

OLA CANVAS x PRETTY BALLADS is a artist series collaboration. Each bag is one of a kind and part of a limited series of 12. Hand printed in Costa Mesa by California and Puerto Rico based artist Pretty Ballads (Diego McElroy).  "Phone-head" print

Product Details

  • Shape: Bonzer (for wider fuller nose boards)
  • Color: Black & Orange 
  • Natural 15oz cotton duck canvas PFD (prepared for dye) 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Cinch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware: Marine grade brass grommets and snaps
  • Width: 23.5"

title: OLA CANVAS X Sean Woolsey Studio - Dive Bomber Campbell Lounge Chair
body_html:
Description

This chair is the result of a collaboration between OLA CANVAS and Sean Woolsey Studio.  The collaboration is built around the iconic Woolsey Studio, Campbell Lounge Chair.  For the collaboration process the chair was deconstructed down to the metal frame and built back up incorporating our design language along the way.  The final product exudes a more luxurious version of two things that are part of the OLA CANVAS design DNA; durability and a love for the ocean.  

Product Details

  • Dimensions: 29"T x 36"D x 29"W
  • Tubular steel frame 
  • Memory foam seat cushion 
  • Fabrics:  Top & back panels of the seat cushions are a off-white 80% polyester 20% cotton herringbone weave with a lux hand feel.  The side panels are a durable but upgraded marine grade nylon dark grey with black micro stripe
  • Hardware: All Marine grade.  Brass grommets & eye snap hooks are 100% brass.  
  • Embroidered OLA CANVAS drive bomber on back seat cushion. (cushion can be flipped to side with no embroidery for a versatile look)

 

The elements that compose the reconstruction of the chair are a mix of military and marine.  The primary frabric, used for the front and back of the cushions, is a lux off-white herringbone fabric with an amazing hand feel.  Herringbone is a classic type of weave used in military apparel and was the first ever “rip-stop” fabric.   The secondary fabric is a heavy duty but upgraded nylon which is used for covers on yachts and sailboats.  The chair is finished with accents found in our bags and other products such as marine grade brass grommets, eye snap hooks and nylon webbing.      

 

Designed in Costa Mesa, CA by OLA CANVAS & Sean Woolsey Studio

title: Olive Drab Bonzer Surfboard Bag
body_html:
BONZER

This bag is called the Bonzer as a homage to the classic fuller nose Bonzer style surfboards. The Bonzer bag is specifically designed to work well with full-nose alternative shapes.  This tough duck canvas bag features a large fin pocket appropriately sized to accommodate up to a 10" fin as well as other items such as wax or sunscreen. 

Product Details

  • Color: Olive Drab (Military Green)
  • Wax coated water repellent 15oz cotton duck canvas 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Cinch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware: Marine grade brass grommets and snaps

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.  Note: for boards with large single fins we suggest that you size up 4"-6." The extra material will ensure the bag fits over your fin. Bag width ranges from 23" to 25.5".

 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by 

OLA CANVAS

title: Olive Drab Full Nose Short Board Bag
body_html:
Olive Drab Wax Coated Water Repellent

15oz Cotton Duck Canvas 

Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G

Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon Pelican Rope with poly core.

Synch/Toggle: Aluminum Crimp Sleeve 

Hardware: 100% marine grade brass grommets

This bag is specifically design to work well for shortboards with fuller noses. (i.e. hypto crypto, baby buggy, biscuit...) Bags are measured from side seam to side seam for width measurement and the number on the bottom left represents the length of the bag from tip of nose to hem stitch. (not the bottom of the bag) which allow's for two more inches of coverage. Designed and made in Costa Mesa CA by 

OLA Canvas

title: Olive Drab Round Nose Surfboard Bag
body_html:
Round Nose 

The Round Nose bag is specifically designed for -you guessed it- round nose boards. Built to accommodate mid-lengths and longboards, this tough duck canvas bag features a large fin pocket appropriately sized to accommodate up to a 10" fin and other small items such as wax or sunscreen. 

Product Details

  • Color: Olive Drab (Military Green)
  • Wax coated water repellent 15oz cotton duck canvas 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Cinch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware:  Marine grade brass grommets and snaps

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.  Note: for boards with large single fins we suggest that you size up 4"-6." The extra material will ensure the bag fits over your fin. Bag width ranges from 24" to 26".  Starting with 24" for 5'8" bags and ending with 26" for 9'6" bags.

 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by 

OLA CANVAS

title: Olive Drab Shortboard Bag
body_html:
Shortboard

The go-to bag for your everyday shortboard.  Specifically tailored to fit most modern shortboard designs.  Slightly fuller in the nose and a little wider in width.  This bag also features a fin pocket to hold your board's fins and other small items such as wax or sunscreen.  

Product Details

  • Color: Olive Drab (Military Green)
  • Wax coated water repellent 15oz cotton duck canvas 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Cinch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware: Marine grade brass grommets and snaps

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.  

 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by 

OLA CANVAS

title: Ranger Brown Bonzer Surfboard Bag
body_html:
BONZER

This bag is called the Bonzer as a homage to the classic fuller nose Bonzer style surfboards. The Bonzer bag is specifically designed to work well with full-nose alternative shapes.  This tough duck canvas bag features a large fin pocket appropriately sized to accommodate up to a 10" fin as well as other items such as wax or sunscreen. 

Product Details

  • Color: Ranger Brown (Khaki Brown)
  • Water repellent 15oz cotton duck canvas 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Cinch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware: Marine grade brass grommets and snaps

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.  Note: for boards with large single fins we suggest that you size up 4"-6." The extra material will ensure the bag fits over your fin.  Bag width ranges from 23" to 25.5".  Starting with 23" for 5'8" bags and ending with 25.5" for 9'6" bags.

 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by 

OLA CANVAS

title: Ranger Brown Full Nose Short Board Bag
body_html:
Ranger Brown Water Repellent

15oz Cotton Duck Canvas 

Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G

Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon Pelican Rope with poly core.

Synch/Toggle: Aluminum Crimp Sleeve 

Hardware: 100% marine grade brass grommets

This bag is specifically design to work well for shortboards with fuller noses. (i.e. hypto crypto, baby buggy, biscuit...) Bags are measured from side seam to side seam for width measurement and the number on the bottom left represents the length of the bag from tip of nose to hem stitch. (not the bottom of the bag) which allow's for two more inches of coverage. Designed and made in Costa Mesa CA by 

OLA Canvas

title: Ranger Brown Round Nose Surfboard Bag
body_html:
Round Nose 

The Round Nose bag is specifically designed for -you guessed it- round nose boards. Built to accommodate mid-lengths and longboards, this tough duck canvas bag features a large fin pocket appropriately sized to accommodate up to a 10" fin and other small items such as wax or sunscreen. 

Product Details

  • Color:Ranger Brown (Khaki Brown)
  • Water repellent 15oz cotton duck canvas 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Cinch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware: Marine grade brass grommets and snaps

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.  Note: for boards with large single fins we suggest that you size up 4"-6." The extra material will ensure the bag fits over your fin. Bag width ranges from 24" to 26".  Starting with 24" for 5'8" bags and ending with 26" for 9'6" bags.

 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by 

OLA CANVAS

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.

title: Sample Natural Shortboard Bag
body_html:
Shortboard

The go-to bag for your everyday shortboard.  Specifically tailored to fit most modern shortboard designs.  Slightly fuller in the nose and a little wider in width.  This bag also features a fin pocket to hold your board's fins and other small items such as wax or sunscreen.  

Product Details

  • Color: Natural (Off White)
  • 15oz cotton duck canvas PFD (prepared for dye) 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Cinch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware: Marine grade brass grommets and snaps

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.

title: Sample OG Boardshort- Black
body_html:
OG BOARDSHORT

Our first boardshort, the OG is made from one of the first tried and true materials for water.  100% Nylon Multi-Ply Taslan. This short has a 16" outseam.  Back patch pocket with button flap closure. Drawstring front closure with button fly. Sizes are hand stamped on interior waistband. Sewn and constructed in Costa Mesa, CA

Product Details

  • Color: Black
  • 100% Nylon taslan weave
  • Outseam 16"
  • Back pocket 
  • Button fly with drawstring closure
  • CA Flag patch on reverse side of left leg 
Designed and Made in California by OLA CANVAS

title: Sample Ranger Brown Shortboard Bag
body_html:
Shortboard

The go-to bag for your everyday shortboard.  Specifically tailored to fit most modern shortboard designs.  Slightly fuller in the nose and a little wider in width.  This bag also features a fin pocket to hold your board's fins and other small items such as wax or sunscreen.  

Product Details

  • Color:Ranger Brown (Khaki Brown)
  • Water repellent 15oz cotton duck canvas 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Drawcord: Black marine grade nylon pelican rope with poly core
  • Cinch/Toggle: Aluminum crimp sleeve 
  • Hardware: Marine grade brass grommets and snaps

A Note About Sizing

Bags come in length increments of 2"-6." If your exact board length is not listed, size up to the next available length.  

 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by 

OLA Canvas

title: SAMPLE Traveler Pouch Natural
body_html:
TRAVELER STORAGE POUCH

The traveler is a top entry storage bag cut from the same cloth as our board bags.

Made for on the go durability and convenience to hold your fins, wax, phone, journal or book.  Thin enough to easily stow in a larger bag or backpack while also being able to hold a book and journal.  This bag is great for your everyday, whether in your hometown or traveling. 

Product Details

  • Color: Natural (Off White)
  • Dimensions:  8.5"H x 10"W
  • 15oz cotton duck canvas PFD (prepared for dye) 
  • Mil Spec. CCC-C-419G
  • Zipper closure w/ ring pull 
  • Hardware: 100% marine grade brass grommets

 

Designed and made in Costa Mesa, CA by 

OLA Canvas

title: Traveler Pouch Natural
body_html:
TRAVELER STORAGE POUCH

The traveler is a top entry storage bag cut from the same cloth as our board bags.

title: UTILITY PANT01- SAIL
body_html:
Inspired from a workwear silhouette but with modern updates for form and function. Made with the same proprietary stretch canvas fabric as our Utility Short01, these pants are made for movement and durability. Relaxed fit with a slightly cropped and tapered leg.

Product Details

  • Color: Sail
  • Stretch canvas fabric with DWR finish
  • Front slash pockets w/ sewn in gussets for easy clipping of tools
  • Double front from mid thigh to mid shin
  • Side detail w/ brass O ring for clip on storage 
  • Double layer seat patch for durability and protection against abrasion  
  • Button fly
  • Slightly cropped and tapered leg

title: UTILITY SHORT 01
body_html:
Inspired from sailing and experiences around the water, we designed this short for the all day everyday. Made from a proprietary stretch canvas fabric that allows for unhindered movement and flexibility while also being highly durable. All details and construction are based around functionality and style.  We've had a blast test driving these for the past year. 

Product Details

  • Color: Black
  • Stretch canvas fabric with DWR finish
  • Front slash pockets w/ sewn in gussets for easy clipping of tools
  • Mesh pocket bags for easy water drainage
  • Double layer seat patch for durability and protection against abrasion  
  • Side detail w/ brass O ring for clip on storage 
  • Button fly
  • Internal waistband drawstring 
  • Outseam 18.5"

title: UTILITY SHORT 01- SAIL
body_html:
Inspired from sailing and experiences around the water, we designed this short for the all day everyday. Made from a proprietary stretch canvas fabric that allows for unhindered movement and flexibility while also being highly durable. All details and construction are based around functionality and style.  We've had a blast test driving these. 

Product Details

  • Color: Sail
  • Stretch canvas fabric with DWR finish
  • Front slash pockets w/ sewn in gussets for easy clipping of tools
  • Mesh pocket bags for easy water drainage
  • Double layer seat patch for durability and protection against abrasion  
  • Side detail w/ brass O ring for clip on storage 
  • Button fly
  • Internal waistband drawstring 
  • Outseam 18.5" 


Designed in California by OLA CANVAS
